321
00:22:10,880 --> 00:22:13,719
So the parents of these children
are working in the cities?

322
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:15,000
Not all of them.

323
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,640
The parents of Mei and Doudou

324
00:22:17,760 --> 00:22:20,079
