356
00:23:40,800 --> 00:23:41,760
Kids.

357
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:42,719
Hello, everyone.

358
00:23:42,800 --> 00:23:43,760
Kids.

359
00:23:46,239 --> 00:23:47,199
Kids,

360
00:23:48,199 --> 00:23:49,880
