487
00:30:28,119 --> 00:30:29,719
The lightning and thunder
didn't scare me.

488
00:30:31,040 --> 00:30:32,719
But you did, by crouching here silently.

489
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:37,880
You are mean.

490
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:39,719
Don't be sarcastic.

491
00:30:40,640 --> 00:30:42,599
