505
00:32:02,119 --> 00:32:03,199
Feeling warmer?

506
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:10,199
Thank you.

507
00:32:15,959 --> 00:32:17,040
Do I look

508
00:32:18,239 --> 00:32:19,920
