509
00:32:24,199 --> 00:32:25,319
Of course not.

510
00:32:26,079 --> 00:32:27,640
I scared myself.

511
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:31,119
You…

512
00:32:31,839 --> 00:32:33,760
