513
00:32:40,760 --> 00:32:42,160
Do you want to talk about it?

514
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:47,199
You look sad.

515
00:32:48,479 --> 00:32:49,959
You were so scared

516
00:32:50,760 --> 00:32:52,040
