567
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:42,959
OK.

568
00:35:46,919 --> 00:35:47,719
Dr. Shao,

569
00:35:48,439 --> 00:35:49,320
would you please

570
00:35:49,479 --> 00:35:50,679
